Class Snake

  • java.lang.Object
    • Snake

  • public class Snake
extends java.lang.Object
    Snake class is a template for snake. Class contains all snake related fields and methods like length and move.

      • checkIfMovePossible

        public boolean checkIfMovePossible​()

        Returns:

      • checkIfAlive

        public boolean checkIfAlive​()
        Checks if snakes is alive. If snakes head goes outside of game board, or touches itself, function sets isAlive variable to false.
        Returns:
        isAlive true if snake is alive.
